{"tid":290613,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好心你哋啲巴士司機啦","createTime":"2017-06-20T01:56:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T15:43:09.000Z","uid":34676,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f71773fb35654571068c0d6db0fc965e181cda9d","tid":290613,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T01:56:06.000Z","msg":"屌你老母咁撚大雨<br />\n你埋站就近啲方便下市民上車啦<br />\n獲獲架車都駛到離開個站位老撚咁遠先停<br />\n焗住又開返把遮行過去上車<br />\n仲要陰陰嘴笑<br />\n我真係屌死哂你班巴士佬"},{"pid":"7f32ceaa2f7efc37dbb42535625d99eed923620d","tid":290613,"uid":25099,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T01:59:02.000Z","msg":"唔笑又話西面;<br />\n笑又話陰陰嘴;<br />\n駛到埋站又話按章工作唔變通;<br />\n要你行兩步上車又話唔方便人,<br />\n你自己渣車返工啦"},{"pid":"86f02f928893eaf88832047a4249496b642be5cd","tid":290613,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T02:00:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔笑又話西面;<br />\n笑又話陰陰嘴;<br />\n駛到埋站又話按章工作唔變通;<br />\n要你行兩步上車又話唔方便人,<br />\n你自己渣車返工啦</blockquote><br />\n喂唔好拉埋我落水<br />\n我一直都覺得駛埋啲係基本野"},{"pid":"6567d33f0804845a33c988e5ba7333a955709dd5","tid":290613,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T02:00:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26619e9f51814ea548b2b7fa78312ed5f984cdb4","tid":290613,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T02:01:27.000Z","msg":"算啦屌  我廢我冇錢<br />\n冇車先要搭巴士<br />\n抵比人撚化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeef98c63efaa8b49902e5858f3b1a964f4d333c","tid":290613,"uid":31269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T02:09:02.000Z","msg":"落咁大雨，仲開到埋咁近個站，一陣淺起左水花，整濕哂啲人，咪一樣要個司機硬食。"},{"pid":"e2897075c8e2997d220cdc36d2de7ef877e042b1","tid":290613,"uid":55327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:43:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}